1. Container kya hai?

Ek lightweight, standalone, executable package jo app ka code + runtime + libraries + settings sab kuch include karta hai
Matlab: Tumhara app jis bhi machine pe chale, same tarike se chalega — "It works on my machine" problem khatam


2. VM (Virtual Machine) vs Container


| Feature         | VM                      | Container                         |
| --------------- | ----------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| **Size**        | GBs (heavy)             | MBs (lightweight)                 |
| **Boot time**   | Minutes                 | Seconds                           |
| **OS**          | Har VM ka apna full OS  | Host OS share karte hain          |
| **Performance** | Slower (OS overhead)    | Fast (bare metal jaisa)           |
| **Isolation**   | Strong (hardware level) | Process level                     |
| **Portability** | Mushkil                 | Easy — same image kahi bhi chalao |


